avenues in the shade of enormous horse chestnut, oaks, and cypress trees (more than 15,000 trees in the park). The oldest tree found here was planted back in 1633!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do madrid El Retiro Park\"><\/noscript><img width=\"241\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best things to do madrid El Retiro Park\" class=\"wp-image-79088 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1370px) 100vw, 1370px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2.jpg 1370w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-428x600.jpg 428w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-578x810.jpg 578w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-241x338.jpg 241w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-548x768.jpg 548w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-731x1024.jpg 731w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-771x1080.jpg 771w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-1028x1440.jpg 1028w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-300x420.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104137\/madrid-2-600x841.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.