onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104208\/madrid-5.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-activities-in-el-retiro\">Activities in El Retiro<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Madrile&#xF1;os come to enjoy the park in the evenings and at weekends, with everyone doing some form of exercise, from running to rollerblading. It&#x2019;s the perfect place to relax under the shade of the trees, especially on Madrid&#x2019;s longer, lighter summer evenings. Because of this, we recommend bringing a picnic and enjoying the late afternoon here after a busy morning of sightseeing.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33.jpg\" alt=\"madrid things to do El Retiro lake\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"287\" alt=\"madrid things to do El Retiro lake\" class=\"wp-image-79223 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-800x511.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-1080x690.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-450x287.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-30x19.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-163x104.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-282x180.jpg 282w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-1024x654.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-1440x920.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-300x192.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-600x383.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-150x96.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33-30x19.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29130200\/madrid-33.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>At the center of El Retiro, you can also discover a beautiful lake where you can hire boats and enjoy the park from the tranquility of the water. They even put on kayaking lessons here! Admire the beautiful palaces and the Alfonso XIII monument (the impressive columns that sit right in front of the lake).<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/76098&amp;media=ht