<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-2-palacio-de-cristal-in-madrid\">2. Palacio de Cristal in Madrid<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Palacio de Cristal (the glass palace) is located at the heart of El Retiro Park. In the shape of a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/greece\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Greek<\/a> cross, this beautiful glass conservatory reaches a height of 22 meters and appears almost out over the water, surrounded by beautiful horse chestnut trees. In the fall, the stunning red and oranges of these colors is really something to see!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29134005\/madrid-36.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"251\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-79229 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1425px) 100vw, 1425px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29134005\/madrid-36.jpg 1425w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29134005\/madrid-36-445x600.jpg 445w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29134005\/madrid-36-601x810.jpg 601w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29134005\/madrid-36-251x338.jpg 251w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29134005\/madrid-36-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29134005\/madrid-36-121x163.jpg 121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29134005\/madrid-36-134x180.jpg 134w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29134005\/madrid-36-570x768.jpg 570w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/