25104153\/madrid-1-241x338.jpg 241w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-548x768.jpg 548w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-731x1024.jpg 731w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-771x1080.jpg 771w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-1028x1440.jpg 1028w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-300x420.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-600x841.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-150x210.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104153\/madrid-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Palace used to be a greenhouse for beautiful flora and fauna. However, it&#x2019;s now owned by the Reina Sofia Museum, which uses it as a unique space to hold art exhibitions throughout the year. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Best of all, it&#x2019;s free to enter, so it&#x2019;s a great thing to do in Madrid. Discover its beautiful ceramic tile floor and the exceptional glass and cast iron frame that holds the building up. Afterward, sit on the charming steps that lead from the Palace into the lake.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6.jpg\" alt=\"El Retiro Park madrid\"><\/noscript><img width=\"448\" height=\"338\" alt=\"El Retiro Park madrid\" class=\"wp-image-79095 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-796x600.jpg 796w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-1074x810.jpg 1074w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-448x338.jpg 448w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-163x123.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-239x180.jpg 239w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-768x579.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-1024x772.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-1432x1080.jpg 1432w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-1909x1440.jpg 1909w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-300x226.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-600x453.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-150x113.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6-30x23.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104223\/madrid-6.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-palacio-cristal-opening-times\">Palacio Cristal Opening Times<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>April to September 10 AM &#x2013; 9 PM and October to March 10 AM &#x2013; 6 PM. Closed on major Spanish holidays.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-3-atocha-renfe-station-in-madrid\">3. Atocha-Renfe Station in Madrid<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Most train stations worldwide aren&#x2019;t really worth seeing, as they&#x2019;re simply used to catch your train to the next destination. However, Atocha Station is the exception! This incredible station is home to a vast tropical garden filled with unique plants and trees that grow to enormous heights and almost reach the top of the station&#x2019;s roof arch. It&#x2019;s strange to see this jungle in an industrial station interior, making it one of the most unique things to do in Madrid!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/madrid-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are all your hotel options in Madrid<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7.jpg\" alt=\"things to do madrid train station\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do madrid train station\" class=\"wp-image-79078 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104026\/madrid-7.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The botanical gardens contain over 7000 plants that originate from all over the globe, from places like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/asia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Asia<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/south-america\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">South America<\/a>, and Australia. There are also information signs so you can learn more about each plant. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> It&#x2019;s a free thing to do in Madrid. Alternatively, if you&#x2019;re traveling somewhere in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Spain<\/a>, arrive at the station 30 minutes early to enjoy the view of this garden.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-79243 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142856\/madrid-38-600