ple, huge murals covering buildings&#x2019; sides. Other works are more discreet, like the miniature artworks or sculptures you&#x2019;ll find hidden down small streets or on doorways. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43.jpg\" alt=\"street art madrid\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"315\" alt=\"street art madrid\" class=\"wp-image-79247 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-800x560.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-1080x755.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-450x315.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-163x114.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-257x180.jpg 257w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-768x537.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-1024x716.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-1440x1007.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-300x210.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-600x420.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29144040\/madrid-43-150x105.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/st