ad\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-150x188.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25141035\/madrid-17.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"entry-fee-opening-times\"><strong>Entry Fee &amp; Opening Times<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Monday &#x2013; Saturday (10 AM &#x2013; 9 PM). Closed Tuesdays. Sunday 10 AM &#x2013; 2.30 PM. In the evenings, visiting the museum is free between 7 PM &#x2013; 9 PM or on Sundays 12.30 PM &#x2013; 2.30 PM. The entry fee is 12 EUR in person at the ticket office or online. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.museoreinasofia.es\/en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book tickets here<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Are you an art lover? Head to the Prado Museum, one of the most famous museums in the world. Incredible works of art are housed here, including renaissance masterpieces. The 200-year-old building itself is a work of art with impressive columns and a grand interior.&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/madrid-prado-museum-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Buy tickets for a guided tour here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-8-plaza-mayor\">8. Plaza Mayor<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Plaza Mayor (main square) is the most famous square in all of Madrid, situated in one of the oldest parts of the city. It&#x2019;s a huge space, measuring 129 meters long and 94 meters wide, used as a meeting point for locals and a place to enjoy a drink in the evening.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/madrid-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are all your hotel options in Madrid<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143154\/madrid-24.jpg\" alt=\"things to do madrid Plaza Mayor\"><\/noscript><img width=\"236\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do madrid Plaza Mayor\" class=\"wp-image-79128 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1341px) 100vw, 1341px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143154\/madrid-24.jpg 1341w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143154\/madrid-24-419x600.jpg 419w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143154\/madrid-24-566x810.jpg 566w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143154\/madrid-24-236x338.jpg 236w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143154\/madrid-24-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143154\/madrid-24-114x163.jpg 114w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143154\/madrid-24-126x180.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143154\/madrid-24-536x768.jpg 536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/