ape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> At Christmas, a fantastic market is held at Plaza Mayor. If you&#x2019;re visiting during this time, enjoy the many stalls surrounding the giant Christmas tree at the center.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-1080x779.jpg\" alt=\"city madrid spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"325\" alt=\"city madrid spain\" class=\"wp-image-79221 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-1080x779.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-800x577.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-450x325.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-163x118.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-250x180.jpg 250w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-768x554.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-1024x739.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-1440x1039.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-300x216.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-600x433.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-150x108.jpg 150w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-30x22.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29125806\/madrid-32-1080x779.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-9-caixa-forum-museum-vertical-garden\">9. Caixa Forum Museum Vertical Garden<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Caixa Forum Museum Vertical Garden is one of the most exciting things to do in Madrid. What was once a power station is now a modern art gallery, complete with a vertical green garden that covers the exterior wall. This interactive garden allows people to touch the 78-foot wall, feel the different textures, and see the 300 different plant species growing here.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31.jpg\" alt=\"madrid things to do Caixa Forum Museum Vertical Garden\"><\/noscript><img width=\"233\" height=\"338\" alt=\"madrid things to do Caixa Forum Museum Vertical Garden\" class=\"wp-image-79196 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1326px) 100vw, 1326px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31.jpg 1326w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-414x600.jpg 414w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-559x810.jpg 559w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-233x338.jpg 233w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-113x163.jpg 113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-124x180.jpg 124w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-530x768.jpg 530w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-707x1024.jpg 707w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-746x1080.jpg 746w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-995x1440.jpg 995w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-300x434.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-600x869.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-150x217.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112134\/madrid-31.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The garden was designed by Patrick Blanc, who is famous for creating these sorts of vertical gardens throughout <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/europe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Europe<\/a>. It&#x2019;s certainly impressive when you consider Madrid&#x2019;s hot, dry summer and the amount of care it takes to keep the garden this green and luscious. In fact, there is no soil on the wall at all, and the plants miraculously survive without it!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"opening-times-and-entry-fee-1\"><strong>Opening Times and Entry Fee<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Open Monday to Sunday 10 AM &#x2013; 8 PM. It&#x2019;s free to see the vertical garden and 6 EUR for the museum. <a href=\"https:\/\/ticketsmadrid.caixaforum.com\/caixaforum_mad\/es_ES\/entradas\/evento\/22568\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Buy tickets online<\/a>. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-10-palacio-real\">10. Palacio Real<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Palacio Real (the Royal Palace) is easily the grandest building in Madrid, surrounded by wide open squares and elegant gardens. You can also see incredible views of the countryside surrounding Madrid from the terrace level. Additionally, you&#x2019;ll get the ambiance of musicians and street artists who come to the square to make money, creating an enjoyable, lively atmosphere. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/madrid-walking-tour-royal-palace\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Join the popular walking tour including a visit to the Royal Palace<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41.jpg\" alt=\"royal palace madrid\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"royal palace madrid\" class=\"wp-image-79241 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141457\/madrid-41-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel