t\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-450x309.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-163x112.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-262x180.jpg 262w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-768x528.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-1024x703.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-1440x989.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-300x206.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-600x412.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-150x103.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29141427\/madrid-39.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Enjoy the ancient exterior and interior, which go back to the 18th century (although the Palace sits on the old site of the medieval Palace that dates back to the 1500s). Visitors can also explore the lavishly decorated rooms with crystal chandeliers, such as the grand armory and the red velvet grandeur of the throne room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"5995P25,22869P86,49144P8\" data-vi-campaign=\"things-to-do-madrid-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            \n\n\n<h4 id=\"opening-times-and-entry-fee\"><strong>Opening Times and Entry Fee<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Monday to Saturday 10 AM &#x2013; 6 PM. Sunday 10 AM&#xA0; &#x2013; 4 PM. However, you can access the gardens until 6 PM. Free access Monday to Thursday 4 PM &#x2013; 6 PM.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Tickets cost 12 EUR. You can also book a guided tour for more information about the Palace&#x2019;s history. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/madrid-royal-palace-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a tour here.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-11-wander-the-streets-of-madrid\">11. Wander the Streets of Madrid<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Arguably one of the best things to do in Madrid is get lost in the maze of beautiful streets. Around every corner, you&#x2019;ll find a new neighborhood, each with its own unique and distinct character. For example, the hipster district of Malasana, the narrow bar-filled lanes of Chueca, or the steep hills of la Latina and Lavapies. Some of the best neighborhoods to enjoy are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-chueca\">Chueca<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"h-the-gay-neighborhood-of-madrid-is-one-of-the-best-and-liveliest-places-to-go-out-with-loads-of-fun-bars-and-squares-where-people-enjoy-tapas-and-drinks\">The gay neighborhood of Madrid is one of the best and liveliest places to go out, with loads of fun bars and squares where people enjoy tapas and drinks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42.jpg\" alt=\"city trip madrid\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"city trip madrid\" class=\"wp-image-79245 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29142914\/madrid-42-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\