\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-79084 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-150x188.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25104110\/madrid-10.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-la-latina\">La Latina<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>La Latina is brimming with history, built on the site of an ancient Islamic fort. Discover its cute churches and steep cobbled hills filled with tapas restaurants. It&#x2019;s a buzzing place on a Saturday and Sunday when the streets are filled with young people and families alike. It&#x2019;s also home to the El Rastro flea market.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26.jpg\" alt=\"beautiful library\"><\/noscript><img width=\"258\" height=\"338\" alt=\"beautiful library\" class=\"wp-image-79132 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1464px) 100vw, 1464px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26.jpg 1464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-458x600.jpg 458w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-618x810.jpg 618w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-258x338.jpg 258w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-124x163.jpg 124w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-137x180.jpg 137w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-586x768.jpg 586w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-781x1024.jpg 781w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-824x1080.jpg 824w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-1098x1440.jpg 1098w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-300x393.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-600x787.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-150x197.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/25143223\/madrid-26.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-barrio-de-las-letras\">Barrio de Las Letras<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The literary neighborhood of Barrio de Las Letras is a place famous for novels and writers, full of charming bookstores, with a distinctly bohemian feel. You&#x2019;ll find the Plaza de Santa Ana and nearby the Calle de las Huertas, full of fun bars at its centre. What&#x2019;s great about Barrio de Las Letras is that many small streets are pedestrianized, so it&#x2019;s perfect for walking around. Plus, it&#x2019;s a little quieter than other neighborhoods.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>If you want to learn more about the history of Madrid, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/madrid-history-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">join this walking tour<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112051\/madrid-27.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do madrid spain streets\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best things to do madrid spain streets\" class=\"wp-image-79190 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112051\/madrid-27.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112051\/madrid-27-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112051\/madrid-27-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112051\/madrid-27-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112051\/madrid-27-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112051\/madrid-27-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112051\/madrid-27-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/26112051\/madrid-27-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/