ing scenes in the whole of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Spain<\/a> are located in Madrid. Whether it&#x2019;s a beer and tapas on a terrace or Michelin star fine dining in a cool rooftop space. Most of all, it&#x2019;s known for being the home of churros and chocolate; there&#x2019;s no better snack after a busy morning of sightseeing! Some of the best restaurants in Madrid are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>FOUR (Delicious lunch!)<\/li><li>Sahuaro Madrid<\/li><li>Alimentacion Quiroga (Local bites &amp; wine)<\/li><li>Grosso Napoletano (Pizza)<\/li><li>Nina Pasta Bar <\/li><li>Nomade Cafe<\/li><li>El Perro De Pavlov (Coffee &amp; Cakes)<\/li><li>Agrado Caf&#xE9; (Coffee &amp; Cakes)<\/li><li>Honest Greens (Veggie)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29135337\/madrid-37.jpg\" alt=\"best restaurant madrid spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best restaurant madrid spain\" class=\"wp-image-79234 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29135337\/madrid-37.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29135337\/madrid-37-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29135337\/madrid-37-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29135337\/madrid-37-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29135337\/madrid-37-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29135337\/madrid-37-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads