d some great budget places to eat if you know where to look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Supermarkets in Spain are very cheap. If you&#x2019;re on a budget, consider making a picnic or buying meals to cook at your accommodation in the evening.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-budget\">\n        <span class=\"block-budget__title\">Budget<\/span><ul class=\"block-budget__list\"><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hotel: 50 &#x2013; 200 EUR \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hostel: 20 &#x2013; 40 EUR \/ night \n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--restaurants\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Price per meal: 5 &#x2013; 25 EUR\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Entrance fees: 5 &#x2013; 15 EUR\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Transport: 3 &#x2013; 10 EUR \/ day\n                    <\/li><\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"besttime\">Best Time to Visit Madrid<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Madrid is a city of contrasts: the winters are very cold, and the summers exceptionally dry and hot. Many local residents leave Madrid in the summer to go to the coast. Because of this, the city becomes quiet, many restaurants close and it can be hard to walk around and see the sights.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For this reason, early spring is a lovely time to visit Madrid or the shoulder months of September\/October. Christmas is also a great time to tick off the top things to do in Madrid and see the Spanish Christmas markets and lights, as long as you&#x2019;re ok with the cold!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"11 Things to do in Madrid Madrid is the capital and biggest city in Spain. Unlike Barcelona, tourism is not its main enterprise; it really is a city for living. Because of that, it&#x2019;s the perfect place to absorb the Spanish way of life and get your &#x2018;culture fix&#x2019; on your trip. Three days is [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":79086,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_relevanssi_hide_post":"","_relevanssi_pin_for_all":"","_relevanssi_pin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_unpin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_include_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_exclude_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_no_append":"","_relevanssi_related_not_related":"","_relevanssi_related_posts":""},"categories":[4750,4750,9,109,109,9],"tags":[78],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v19.3 (Yoast SEO v19.7.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Best Things to do in Madrid